    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.42857143;
  }

   div.faq-panel.show {
    opacity: 1;
    max-height: 750px;
   }

   div.mobile-faq-panel {
    {% comment %} background-color: white; {% endcomment %}
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: 0.6s ease-in-out;
    opacity: 0;
    text-align: left;
    padding-left: 18px;
   }

   div.mobile-faq-panel.show {
      opacity: 1;
    max-height: 750px;
   }

   .caption-with-letter-spacing {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
</style>

<section
  class="faq-section"
  style="background-color: #e8f4fa; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 7rem; padding-bottom: 7rem;"
>
  <div class="collapsible-content__header scroll-trigger animate--slide-in" style="text-align: center;">
    <p class="caption-with-letter-spacing">Frequently Asked Questions</p>

    <h2
      class="collapsible-content__heading inline-richtext h1"
      style="font-size: calc(var(--font-heading-scale)* 2.4rem) !important; margin-top: 10px;"
    >
      FAQs
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div style="max-width: 120rem; justify-content: center; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
    <div class="mobile-expertise-faq">
      <div>
        <h3 class="mobile-faq-menu">General</h3>
        <div class="mobile-faq-panel">
          <div class="expertise-faq">
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">Is HitNeon legitimate?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  Yes, HitNeon is a 100% legitimate business, specializing in high-quality Neon LED signs that can be
                  customized according to our customers' preferences. We are committed to delivering the perfect
                  solutions, ensuring a secure and satisfying shopping experience. Our focus is on bringing personalized
                  flair to your spaces with our bespoke Neon Sign products, alongside our dedication to customer
                  satisfaction and service.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">Why choose HitNeon for neon signs?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  We specialize in crafting high-quality personalized neon signs that are not only vibrant and
                  eye-catching but also tailored to meet your preferences and needs. Our signs are also energy-efficient
                  and durable. Additionally, we pride ourselves on our responsive and helpful customer service team, so
                  rest assured your experience will be smooth and enjoyable all the way.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">What is the difference between LED neon and glass neon?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  LED neon signs are more durable and energy-efficient, which makes them a safer and more cost-effective
                  choice. LED neon is made from flexible tubing that's less prone to breaking and easier to install and
                  maintain. Additionally, LED signs offer more customization options and a longer lifespan compared to
                  their glass counterparts. While both have their aesthetic appeal, the practical benefits of LED neon
                  make it a popular choice for modern needs.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">Do you have a warranty? What does the warranty include?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  Yes, we offer a 2-year warranty on our products. This warranty covers any defects in materials and
                  workmanship. In the rare event that you encounter an issue with your product due to our manufacturing
                  process, we will provide a replacement at no extra cost. Please read through our
                  <a href="/policies/refund-policy">Refund and Cancellation Policy</a> for more details or feel free to
                  reach out to us at <a href="mailto:hello@hitneon.com">hello@hitneon.com</a> for all your questions.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">Are neon signs safe for use in homes with children or pets?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  Absolutely. Most neon signs used today are LED neon signs, which are safe for homes with children and
                  pets. They use low voltage and flexible materials, unlike traditional glass neon signs. Just be sure
                  to place the sign where curious hands and playful paws can't reach it.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="mobile-faq-menu">Shipping and Returns</h3>
        <div class="mobile-faq-panel">
          <div class="expertise-faq">
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">What is the lead time for custom neon signs?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  We need 3-4 business days to manufacture your custom neon sign, and shipment usually takes another 2
                  business days. So, you can expect to receive your sign in 5 to 6 business days in total.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">What to do if there is a missing item in my package?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  If there is a missing item or a problem with your package, please contact us at
                  <a href="mailto:hello@hitneon.com">hello@hitneon.com</a> immediately, and we’ll take care of the rest.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">How do returns and exchanges work?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  We have a very easy and convenient return and exchange process. Please visit our
                  <a href="/policies/refund-policy">Returns & Exchanges</a> page for more information on the next step.
                  You can always contact us through email or phone if you need further help. Our dedicated customer
                  service will do its best to help you.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">What does the packaging include?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  The packaging includes your made-to-order neon sign, power supply/adapter, complimentary dimmer,
                  installation kit as well as the instruction guide on how to install your sign in a matter of minutes.
                  To make things easier for you, we came up with the easiest installation process there is.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">Can neon signs be shipped outside the US and Canada?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  Yes, we ship worldwide with free express shipping. The shipping takes 2-3 business days for UK and
                  Europe. For the rest of the world shipping time is 2-5 business days. Please note that there may be
                  Customs and Duty fees at your home country which falls under buyer’s responsibility. Please check the
                  Customs requirements for your country before placing your order.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="mobile-faq-menu">Installation</h3>
        <div class="mobile-faq-panel">
          <div class="expertise-faq">
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">How long is the cord for the neon signs?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  The cord for our neon signs is 6 feet long. This thoughtful length gives you the flexibility you need
                  to find the perfect spot for your sign. Whether you have a specific design layout in mind or want some
                  freedom in placement, the cord ensures that you can easily reach a power outlet.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">How can I clean my neon sign?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  We include a cleaning guide in every package we ship, but in case you have lost it, here is the
                  cleaning process in a few easy steps:<br>

                  1. To clean your neon sign, first ensure it is turned off and unplugged from the power source for
                  safety.<br>
                  2. Gently wipe the surface with a soft, dry cloth to remove dust. If needed, you can slightly dampen
                  the cloth with water but avoid using harsh chemicals or abrasive cleaners that could damage the sign.<br>
                  3. After wiping, if you've used a damp cloth, gently dry the sign with another soft, dry cloth.<br>
                  It's important to handle the sign gently during cleaning to prevent any bending or breaking of its
                  parts. Regular cleaning will help maintain the sign's brightness and durability.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">What maintenance does neon signs require?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  Neon signs from HitNeon are designed to be easy to maintain. Regular dusting with a soft, dry cloth is
                  generally all that's needed to keep your sign looking its best. It's important to handle the sign
                  gently, especially when moving or adjusting it, to protect the neon tubing and electrical components.
                  Ensure the sign is operated according to the instructions and connected to an appropriate power
                  source. Avoid exposing the sign to moisture as this can damage the electronics. Also, periodically
                  inspect the power connections and cords for wear or damage, and replace them as necessary. With these
                  simple care steps, your neon sign will continue to illuminate your space beautifully for years.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="mobile-faq-menu">Technical</h3>
        <div class="mobile-faq-panel">
          <div class="expertise-faq">
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">What are the backboard options for neon signs?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  At HitNeon, we offer four different backboard options. “Cut to Shape” and “Cut to Letter” are the most
                  popular of these four. We also offer “Full Acrylic Board” and “Free Standing” options to make sure you
