                  black, red and blue.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">What are the available color options for neon signs?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  HitNeon offers 10 different colors for neon signs: white, warm white, yellow, orange, red, pink,
                  purple, blue, green and ice blue. If you need a custom color, feel free to reach out, and we’ll try to
                  make it happen. Multi-color signs are also available at an extra cost.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">What are neon signs made of?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  Neon signs from HitNeon are primarily made using LED technology. The "neon" part of the sign is
                  crafted from flexible LED neon tubing, which is a durable and energy-efficient alternative to
                  traditional glass neon. This tubing is made of materials that are both flexible and resilient,
                  allowing for a wide range of custom shapes and designs. Inside the tubing, LED lights provide the
                  bright, vibrant glow that mimics the classic neon look. The signs are often mounted on backboards,
                  which can be made of various materials depending on the design and customer preferences.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">How are neon signs powered?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  Neon signs are mainly powered by electricity. They are designed to be plugged into a standard
                  electrical outlet using a power adapter. The LED technology in these signs is highly energy-efficient,
                  consuming significantly less power than traditional glass neon signs. If you need to use your sign
                  outdoors where no electric outlet is available, we also offer a battery box at additional cost.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">Can neon signs be used outdoors?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  We offer neon signs for both indoor and outdoor use. Our indoor signs are designed to create a vibrant
                  atmosphere inside your home or business. While they're not built to withstand rain, they'll last a
