            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">What fonts are available for custom neon signs?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  We have 20+ fonts for you to choose from. If you have a particular neon sign font in mind, feel free
                  to email us, and we’ll see if it’s doable.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">Can I use my logo for a custom neon sign?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  Sure thing. Visit our
                  <a href="/pages/custom-designed-led-neon-sign">custom artwork neon sign</a> page. Submit your logo or
                  artwork, along with other requested information. We’ll promptly provide you with a quote and a free
                  mock-up, so you can see what it’ll look like. Upon your confirmation, you can complete your purchase.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">How much does a custom neon sign cost?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  At HitNeon, we're passionate about creating high-quality neon signs at competitive prices. As a direct
                  manufacturer, we cut out the middleman, allowing us to offer you the best value possible. This means
                  you get exceptional quality at a budget-friendly price. Plus, with our transparent pricing, you'll see
