                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="faq-accordion">How can I get a quote for a custom neon sign with a logo?</h3>
              <div class="faq-panel">
                <p class="faq-panel" style="margin-top: 1.25em; margin-bottom: 2.5em">
                  Visit our <a href="/pages/custom-designed-led-neon-sign">custom artwork neon sign</a> page. Simply
